name: Alice/Breaker
description: Alice felt an overpowering boredom as she sat next to the river. Seemingly out of nowhere, she spotted a white rabbit scurry off in a hurry. She was compelled to follow the creature.

name: Snow White/Breaker
description: The mirror drove the girl mad. So many people were captivated by her beauty. She went to meet the prince, and yet...

name: Red Riding Hood/Crusher
description: It was intended to be an easy task. It was just a simple meal, after all. But the tale never unfolds that way. When an incorrectly buttoned shirt was noticed too late...

name: Cinderella/Gunner
description: While she largely accepted it, her life was nothing but misery...\nUntil a fairy took pity on the meak girl and cast a spell on her.\nThat was when the no longer helpless girl realized what strength and power truly were...

name: Pinocchio/Crusher
description: The puppet Geppetto made was a mere misfit. Pinocchio desperately struggled through life with the hope of becoming a real boy. But would his wish ever come true?

name: Sleeping Beauty/Crusher
description: A "blessing" and a "curse."\nHer life was ruled by conflicting wishes.\nWhat tale awaits the girl who wakes from a 100-year slumber?

name: Gretel/Breaker
description: The siblings got lost in the forest. The old woman in a gingerbread house patiently awaited their arrival.\nTheir love got them through that ordeal.\nBut the real terror awaited elsewhere...

name: Princess Kaguya/Paladin
description: The bamboo cutter's heart raced in his chest.\nHe couldn't shake the feeling that there was something else in the forest.\nHis fears were realized when he cut open a shining stalk of bamboo and found a girl inside.

He was the one who cursed me.
A grand and senile doll now...
How many more holy nights until he
returns to his original form?

name: Three Little Pigs/Sorcerer
description:
Everyone is different, everyone is good.
If only they could think that way.
But these three need exactly the right
body to be satisfied.
And so...

name: Alice/Diva
description: Alice felt an overpowering boredom as she sat next to the river. Seemingly out of nowhere, she spotted a white rabbit scurry off in a hurry. She was compelled to follow the creature.

name: Rapunzel/Diva
description: The little bird sang.\nFor the sake of its parent.\nBut at some point, the little bird's song was not what its parents had wished.

name: Sleeping Beauty/Diva
description: A "blessing" and a "curse."\nHer life was ruled by conflicting wishes.\nWhat tale awaits the girl who wakes from a 100-year slumber?

name: Snow White/Slime
description: The mirror drove the girl mad. So many people were captivated by her beauty. She went to meet the prince, and yet...

name: Gretel/Yukata
description: The siblings got lost in the forest. The old woman in a gingerbread house patiently awaited their arrival.\nTheir love got them through that ordeal.\nBut the real terror awaited elsewhere...

name: Red Riding Hood/Yukata
description: It was intended to be an easy task. It was just a simple meal, after all. But the tale never unfolds that way. When an incorrectly buttoned shirt was noticed too late...

name: Hamelin/Yukata
description: The piper plays his pipe.\nTrampling over the unsightly before it reaches his sight.\nFor his song is only for the beautiful.
